{"tid":1392992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我想問幾千萬抗爭基金可唔可以資助義士買裝備， 可唔可以提供裝備畀前線？","createTime":"2019-08-01T02:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T04:02:08.000Z","uid":43785,"like":4,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fced09a6b3219379d3c962dcdfd8596701992639","tid":1392992,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:41:56.000Z","msg":"我想問籌左個幾千萬抗爭基金， 條數係點樣運作我真係唔撚想知啦。<br />\n但可唔可以資助義士買裝備，買甲買盾買豬咀買同一套黑衫， 甚至可唔可以提供裝備，軍火等等畀前線？<br />\n<br />\n依家前線面對嘅困難越嚟越多，警方裝備不停升級，728裝備睇得到完全係不足。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以幫幫手推，我地俾錢唔係要你善後，依家要叫佢地提供支援給前線開戰，我地要贏，唔係要輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n我地發夢有好裝備，就唔洗輸，更唔會俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7910f60937750c9aec232c9c25a19ab9c9f602bd","tid":1392992,"uid":54181,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:43:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6328b6d8904b24f6246ae6737dd34f757ed08d58","tid":1392992,"uid":173814,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:44:37.000Z","msg":"人地有名有姓，買裝備俾前線應該可以拉人封艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再加上連基本法律支援都未必夠，要再分舊錢黎買野可能有難度。<br />\n<br />\n我相信香港人最多就係錢，不如自發處理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef03310bfe877ddf59b69aa4b35386fb60668d76","tid":1392992,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:45:19.000Z","msg":"可以凍結你戶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c08e5eb48486e842edde9ac5ed5a3ff4d71997a","tid":1392992,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:45:21.000Z","msg":"講撚咗唔買得裝備"},{"pid":"612374414a83d77572a0e900785734538721d24f","tid":1392992,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c08e5eb48486e842ed